# # Configuration
#
# - Overview https://ghostty.org/docs/config
#    - if `$XDG_CONFIG_HOME` is not defined, it defaults to `$HOME/.config/ghostty/config`
#    - macOS only: `$HOME/Library/Application\ Support/com.mitchellh.ghostty/config`
# - Option Reference https://ghostty.org/docs/config/#configuration-options
#
# Combine multiple configuration files by using the `config-file` option.
#
# ```
# config-file = some/relative/sub/config
# config-file = ?optional/config
# config-file = /absolute/path/config
# ```

